{"tid":23692,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"撈麵叫撈麵，點解烏冬撈會叫烏冬撈","createTime":"2016-12-05T05:55:14.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-05T06:47:06.000Z","uid":54819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2f24c22674f6d5d01ace3c854d7c8ec14c03e544","tid":23692,"uid":54819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:55:14.000Z","msg":"之前開錯左喺吹水台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n次次去七仔買都要諗勁耐究竟係 撈烏冬 定 烏冬撈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n明明撈麵叫撈麵，烏冬撈點解會唔跟返個pattern<br />\n<br />\n之前同人討論過，有兩個推測<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1. 其實烏冬撈全名係&quot;烏冬撈麵&quot;，但個麵字省略左，同炸醬撈一樣<br />\n<br />\n2. 七仔要美化撈烏冬呢樣野 (其實我都唔知係咪七仔發明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )，所以改個有啲日本feel嘅名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同關東煮一樣個動詞擺喺名詞後面<br />\n<br />\n咁多位巴打點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c02b6a801960b29523d33107114d187b9887d45","tid":23692,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:56:37.000Z","msg":"聽開撈烏冬啵"},{"pid":"0bccd634f157e1326beabbdd35dad97bee9621f5","tid":23692,"uid":21886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:57:45.000Z","msg":"烏撈冬"},{"pid":"760d466b8e9ae65c309d2488bc29148b09d93216","tid":23692,"uid":47966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:58:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>烏撈冬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n烏撈單冬"},{"pid":"cb656badc1541fc0dfe7d5ed61ffae988bb659c8","tid":23692,"uid":36501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:59:13.000Z","msg":"其實叫烏don&rsquo;t know"},{"pid":"4298efa47dfd8d779fbd2432373264c6915e4f96","tid":23692,"uid":17359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T06:01:20.000Z","msg":"海底撈"},{"pid":"0a52ce87129a86ca82051944e68c367784e3cdba"