"uid":54819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T06:41:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>因為麵撈係另一種野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/奶油炒麵糊\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E5%A5%B6%E6%B2%B9%E7%82%92%E9%BA%B5%E7%B3%8A&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=4da0889c\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/奶油炒麵糊</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但正常中文係 動詞+名詞 架播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我當左 撈麵 同 撈烏冬 係正常嘅名<br />\n<br />\n冇記錯的話，撈麵好似係叫動賓結構<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a546234e9db0d20389862ffbe78d6dc56b2ac50","tid":23692,"uid":31542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T06:42:37.000Z","msg":"艾冬撈"},{"pid":"17d643cfc3e700159541c9482111fbe87a499d7c","tid":23692,"uid":52759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T06:43:01.000Z","msg":"個撈字好怪"},{"pid":"c889067678634243ef8dcdca7e93a0be5a30ccdf","tid":23692,"uid":46393,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T06:47:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個撈字好怪</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同一時間睇到太多同一個字 個字會變得陌生"}]}